Header.title: Ouakhila Torou
Header.paragraph: I am a Junior Software Developer, Travel Photographer and part time content creator.

About.paragraph: Hello! My name is Ouakhila. Wakila is the correct pronunciation. I am a computer science student from the Benin Republic studying in the United Kingdom. I am very interested in visual arts. I'll walk you through all of my storytelling videos as a content creator, as well as any significant events in my life.
